   "x": 60,
   "y": 64,
   "width": 1000,
   "height": 22,
   "text": "\uc2e4\uc81c \uad6c\ud604: admission gate \u2192 cache attach \u2192 item packing (\ub2e8\uc77c \uc778\ucf54\ub529 \uc9c0\uc810) \u2192 selected-only H2D \u2192 store/finalize + cache write-through \u2192 \ub3d9\uc77c-step LLM",
