  {
   "type": "text",
   "id": "adm_startup_t",
   "x": 916,
   "y": 198,
   "width": 610,
   "height": 60,
   "text": "supports = isinstance(model, MultimodalModelMixin) AND processor capability\neffective tokens = max(configured \ub610\ub294 LLM fallback, model atomic maximum)\ncapacity \u2192 Q2.5: processor geometry; Q3: tokens/merge; Pixtral: min(items,tokens/merge)\nprofiling \u2192 effective budget \uc548\uc5d0\uc11c long-item + many-item boundary\ub97c \uc21c\ucc28 \uc2e4\ud589",
   "originalText": "supports = isinstance(model, MultimodalModelMixin) AND processor capability\neffective tokens = max(configured \ub610\ub294 LLM fallback, model atomic maximum)\ncapacity \u2192 Q2.5: processor geometry; Q3: tokens/merge; Pixtral: min(items,tokens/merge)\nprofiling \u2192 effective budget \uc548\uc5d0\uc11c long-item + many-item boundary\ub97c \uc21c\ucc28 \uc2e4\ud589",
   "fontSize": 11,
   "fontFamily": 3,
